sentence.text: Furthermore, positive regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II is associated with unfavorable overall survival (n=866, p=0.004) and represents an independent prognostic factor (HR=2.36, p=0.000) in lung adenocarcinoma (negative regulation of protein catabolic process) patients, but is not associated with overall survival of squamous cell carcinoma (negative regulation of peptidase activity) patients (n=524, p=0.27).
